msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Se sètz en fòra dels EUA, vos recomanam NOWPayments (frais mai baixos, "
"dirècte a vòstre pòrtier). Se sètz dins los EUA, Stripe Crypto es tanben una"
" opcion. Podètz activar mantunas prestacions e deixar vòstres visitaires de "
"causir!"

