msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Los pagaments crypto de Stripe (USDC) son NOMÉS disponibles solament per las"
" entrepresas basadas a los EUA. Se sètz en fòra dels EUA, Stripe acceptarà "
"solament pagaments per carta de crèdit al vòstre saldo Stripe (pas "
"diretcament al crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Se sètz als EUA, podètz utilizar Stripe per recebre crypto dirèctament. Se "
"sètz fòra, considèri NOWPayments o CoinGate per pagaments direts en crypto."

