msgid "Let My Girl Friend Enjoy Our Coffee"
msgstr "Permet a ma amiga de femel de gaudir nòstre cafè"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Un widget de donacions e pagaments poderós e gratuit que permet a vòstres "
"visitaires de vos donar per carta de crèdit o criptò (Quai). Pas de taxes "
"mensilhas, pas de subscripcions de tercaires – unicament vòstre portari e "
"servicis gratuïts."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Qualques navigadors blòquan los scripts de tercaires per privacitat. Aqueste"
" proxy carga los scripts per vòstre pròpriu servidor per esquivar aquestes "
"blòques."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Podètz metre a jorn los URLs dels scripts d'aicí jos se los URLs originaus "
"cambian o se volètz usar un CDN diferent."

